## Conclusion
Common network security threats such as DoS attacks, Man-in-the-Middle attacks, and IP Spoofing can significantly impact organizations and individuals. By understanding how these attacks operate and implementing appropriate security measures, organizations can strengthen their network defenses and protect valuable information.
